    <item>
      <title>神田表示日本将对过度的外汇波动采取适当措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/kanda-says-japan-to-take-appropriate-steps-on-excessive-fx-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首席货币官员神田正人(Masato Kanda)重申了他的立场，即在日元贬值至三周以来的最低水平后，将采取不成比例的货币走势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/kanda-says-japan-to-take-appropriate-steps-on-excessive-fx-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 16:09:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油公司债务上限威胁后哥伦比亚债券和比索下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/colombia-bonds-peso-drop-after-petro-threats-over-debt-ceiling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗威胁称，如果立法者拒绝批准提高该国债务上限，他将“停止付款”，导致哥伦比亚债券和货币暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/colombia-bonds-peso-drop-after-petro-threats-over-debt-ceiling</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 15:03:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储沃勒表示，他仍然认为中性利率相对较低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/fed-s-waller-says-factors-that-lowered-neutral-rate-may-reverse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事克里斯托弗·沃勒表示，他仍然认为中性利率相对较低，但他警告说，不可持续的财政支出可能会改变这一趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/fed-s-waller-says-factors-that-lowered-neutral-rate-may-reverse</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 13:20:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
